Data

The first line was removed from each of the log files for proper headers of data. Row with NaN values removed. Change ‘Time’ to ‘dates’. Dates should be ordered in ascending date (oldest to newest).

IAV_H1 <- read.csv("gisaid_IAV_H1_skyride.txt", sep ='\t', header = TRUE)
IAV_H1$dates <- as.Date(paste(format(date_decimal(IAV_H1$dates),"%Y-%m-%d")))

IAV_H3 <- read.csv("gisaid_IAV_H3_skyride.txt", sep ='\t', header = TRUE)
